Aiping, Qiming, come here.

25
00:01:42,370 --> 00:01:43,520
Come in.

26
00:01:44,290 --> 00:01:45,770
Honeysuckle and chrysanthemum.

27
00:01:46,160 --> 00:01:47,010
Alright.

28
00:01:47,090 --> 00:01:48,160
I like them.

29
00:01:48,290 --> 00:01:49,130
Auntie,

30
00:01:49,440 --> 00:01:50,590
how have you been these days?

31
00:01:52,160 --> 00:01:53,000
Watermelon?

32
00:01:53,490 --> 00:01:54,520
I bought it just for you.

33
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,090
- Careful, it's heavy.
- It's heavy.

34
00:01:57,570 --> 00:01:58,770
It's an 8424 watermelon, right?

35
00:02:01,800 --> 00:02:03,290
- It's ripe.
- It's ripe.

36
00:02:03,290 --> 00:02:04,200
- Nanny,
- Definitely.

37
00:02:04,490 --> 00:02:05,490
cut it and let's eat.

38
00:02:05,770 --> 00:02:08,120
Alright. Boss, I'll cut it for you soon.

39
00:02:09,090 --> 00:02:10,280
Why are you so late?

40
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:12,000
I've been waiting so long.

41
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,730
It's only been two days
and you miss me so much?

42
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,680
Is she your girlfriend?

43
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,370
Chairwoman Liao,

44
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:20,800
don't you recognize me?

45
00:02:20,890 --> 00:02:21,730
Yes, I do.

46
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:22,840
I know you.

47
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:25,520
When are you getting married?

48
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:31,840
It's still too early.

49
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:32,890
No rush.

50
00:02:32,890 --> 00:02:33,730
We're not in a hurry.

51
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:36,050
You're not, but I am.

52
00:02:36,370 --> 00:02:37,330
I'm in a hurry.

53
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:38,520
Jianguo,

54
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:40,840
when are you getting married?

55
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:42,240
You should hurry up.

56
00:02:42,370 --> 00:02:43,450
I can't wait any longer.

57
00:02:43,450 --> 00:02:44,960
I want to attend your wedding,

58
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:45,800
you know?

59
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:47,800
Auntie,

60
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:48,680
who am I?

61
00:02:49,490 --> 00:02:50,330
Jianguo.

62
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:54,170
Hongying.

63
00:02:54,490 --> 00:02:55,930
Your girlfriend, right?

64
00:02:57,170 --> 00:02:58,010
Hongying...

65
00:02:58,170 --> 00:02:59,240
Okay.

66
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:00,280
Mom,

67
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:02,280
don't make things complicated.

68
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,720
This is Zhang Qiming,

69
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:05,930
Little San.

70
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:07,210
This is Guan Aiping,

71
00:03:07,210 --> 00:03:08,450
the Aiping from next door.

72
00:03:08,540 --> 00:03:10,140
- You're messing around.
- No, I'm not!

73
00:03:12,170 --> 00:03:13,120
Jianjun didn't

74
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:14,960
have a banquet, did he?

75
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:16,240
No, there wasn't.

76
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:17,610
So for Jianguo's wedding,

77
00:03:17,610 --> 00:03:19,090
why don't we have a banquet?

78
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:20,720
Foreign weddings don't count.

79
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:22,490
You must have a banquet.

80
00:03:22,490 --> 00:03:23,930
If not, I'll beat you up.

81
00:03:24,170 --> 00:03:25,090
Calm down.

82
00:03:25,090 --> 00:03:26,730
We will.

83
00:03:26,930 --> 00:03:27,770
We'll get married.

84
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,120
Hongying,

85
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,240
let me tell you...

86
00:03:34,890 --> 00:03:35,890
She's just like this now.

87
00:03:36,090 --> 00:03:37,120
My friend told me

88
00:03:37,140 --> 00:03:38,560
that a specialist on Huashan Road

89
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:39,840
is good at treating this disease.

90
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:40,840
Take Auntie there.

91
00:03:43,770 --> 00:03:44,610
Cut the watermelon.

92
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:47,170
It's brittle.

93
00:03:47,170 --> 00:03:48,010
Take it slow.

94
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:50,120
Are you feeling hot?

95
00:03:50,650 --> 00:03:51,490
I'll fan you.

96
00:03:51,770 --> 00:03:52,650
Let me help you.

97
00:03:54,370 --> 00:03:55,610
It's hot now.

98
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:58,120
There's an electric fan.

99
00:04:03,930 --> 00:04:04,930
Did your mom really think

100
00:04:04,930 --> 00:04:06,090
he's her son?

101
00:04:07,050 --> 00:04:08,490
"My mind is very clear.

102
00:04:08,490 --> 00:04:09,960
Don't lie to me."

103
00:04:10,740 --> 00:04:12,920
Then she turned her head
and took Zhang Qiming's hand.

104
00:04:13,300 --> 00:04:14,310
I'll cooperate.

105
00:04:14,330 --> 00:04:15,520
"Jianguo,

106
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:17,480
when are you getting married?"

107
00:04:17,960 --> 00:04:19,280
Mistaken him for Jianguo.

108
00:04:19,280 --> 00:04:20,640
So, how did you explain it to her?

109
00:04:20,640 --> 00:04:21,660
How else could we explain?

110
00:04:21,660 --> 00:04:22,720
We just coaxed her.

111
00:04:23,210 --> 00:04:24,050
The wontons are here.

112
00:04:24,060 --> 00:04:25,600
Thanks, Ms. Huang.

113
00:04:27,770 --> 00:04:29,280
Actually, my mom

114
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:31,330
always has a concern, right?

115
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:33,480
Her two sons went to America

116
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:35,890
and got married without inviting her.

117
00:04:36,130 --> 00:04:37,280
When they had kids,

118
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:38,520
they didn't even ask her.

119
00:04:38,650 --> 00:04:40,720
Let's not mention your brothers, okay?

120
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,600
I'm furious

121
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:42,920
when you talk about them.

122
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:44,210
How could they do that?

123
00:04:44,810 --> 00:04:46,330
It's not all their fault.

124
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:47,360
America is

125
00:04:47,650 --> 00:04:48,890
too far away from us.

126
00:04:49,690 --> 00:04:50,890
Besides,

127
00:04:50,890 --> 00:04:52,450
their conditions are not so good.

128
00:04:54,840 --> 00:04:56,340
- Chairwoman Liao.
- Hello, everyone.

129
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:57,650
Hello.

130
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,320
Jianguo,

131
00:04:59,500 --> 00:05:00,350
Hongying,

132
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,450
you're all here.

133
00:05:02,280 --> 00:05:03,570
I was looking for you.

134
00:05:04,330 --> 00:05:05,960
We're having a happy occasion.

135
00:05:06,330 --> 00:05:08,160
Jianguo and Hongying
are getting married.

136
00:05:09,090 --> 00:05:11,280
That's right. Congratulations to us.

137
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:13,520
- Congrats, congrats to Jianguo.
- Thank you.

138
00:05:13,810 --> 00:05:15,520
Mom insisted on coming to find you.

139
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:17,480
She insisted on giving this to you.

140
00:05:17,650 --> 00:05:18,490
To me?

141
00:05:19,130 --> 00:05:20,090
Mr. Driver,

142
00:05:20,090 --> 00:05:21,040
thank you very much.

143
00:05:21,520 --> 00:05:22,600
You should leave.

144
00:05:23,010 --> 00:05:24,600
It's hot out. I need air-conditioning.

145
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:27,060
Mom, what did you give me?

146
00:05:27,060 --> 00:05:27,900
Nanny.

147
00:05:28,250 --> 00:05:29,090
Call me Nanny.

148
00:05:30,250 --> 00:05:31,130
You've worked

149
00:05:31,130 --> 00:05:32,250
for a lot of people.

150
00:05:32,650 --> 00:05:34,520
You have more connections than me.

151
00:05:35,010 --> 00:05:35,920
Do you know

152
00:05:36,090 --> 00:05:37,160
where's the best place

153
00:05:37,330 --> 00:05:39,330
to hold a banquet in Shanghai?

154
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,570
I'll ask around.

155
00:05:41,740 --> 00:05:43,130
If Jianguo and Hongying get married,

156
00:05:43,280 --> 00:05:44,720
I'll pay for the banquet.

157
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,280
That's amazing!

158
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,600
This is money.

159
00:05:48,690 --> 00:05:49,530
It's money.

160
00:05:51,130 --> 00:05:51,970
Alright.

161
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:52,880
Understood, Boss.

162
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:54,690
So, Chen Jian...

163
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:55,760
No.

164
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:57,720
Mom gave it.

165
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,200
Chen Jianguo,

166
00:06:00,210 --> 00:06:01,360
this is the wedding fund

167
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,890
from your mom,

168
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:04,920
my boss,

169
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,720
for you and Hongying.

170
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:08,130
Okay, I'll accept it.

171
00:06:08,130 --> 00:06:09,160
Return it to Auntie.

172
00:06:09,810 --> 00:06:10,920
- Open it.
- Open it.

173
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:11,890
Let me open it for you.

174
00:06:11,890 --> 00:06:12,920
Count it.

175
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:13,760
Count it, okay.

176
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:17,760
See?

177
00:06:17,770 --> 00:06:18,840
So much cash.

178
00:06:18,960 --> 00:06:20,400
I've been saving it for a long time.

179
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,690
Count it now.

180
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:24,880
Count it.

181
00:06:25,330 --> 00:06:27,090
I stay at home all day.

182
00:06:27,140 --> 00:06:28,430
I don't know what's going on now.

183
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,890
I'm not sure if it's enough.

184
00:06:30,010 --> 00:06:30,850
It's enough, right?

185
00:06:32,770 --> 00:06:33,610
Let me count it.

186
00:06:38,960 --> 00:06:40,600
It's plenty, more than needed.

187
00:06:41,770 --> 00:06:43,040
I knew it was enough.

188
00:06:43,210 --> 00:06:44,050
Jianguo,

189
00:06:44,300 --> 00:06:45,400
so when are you and Hongying

190
00:06:45,400 --> 00:06:46,770
going to

191
00:06:47,330 --> 00:06:48,210
have the banquet?

192
00:06:59,890 --> 00:07:01,360
Are we really going to have a banquet?

193
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,960
That's what I'm thinking.

194
00:07:04,450 --> 00:07:06,920
A troubled heart needs a heartfelt cure.

195
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:09,330
Xiu'e also mentioned

196
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,210
that Auntie didn't attend

197
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:13,520
either of her sons' weddings.

198
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,650
It's the biggest regret of her life.

199
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:18,570
Let's host a lively banquet.

200
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:19,840
It might help

201
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:21,890
improve her health.

202
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:25,280
I'm not doing this for myself.

203
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:26,280
I can wait.

204
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:27,650
No problem at all.

205
00:07:27,890 --> 00:07:29,690
I know Han is in high school.

206
00:07:29,890 --> 00:07:32,770
And you just apprenticed under Dr. Zhan.

207
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:35,040
In a year, Han will be in college.

208
00:07:35,690 --> 00:07:38,450
And you, Dr. Guan,
will finish your training in four years.

209
00:07:39,130 --> 00:07:40,210
I can wait for all that.

210
00:07:41,090 --> 00:07:42,010
I'm really

211
00:07:42,330 --> 00:07:43,400
worried about her.

212
00:07:43,650 --> 00:07:44,490
I'm afraid of...

213
00:07:45,400 --> 00:07:46,240
Qiming.

214
00:07:55,210 --> 00:07:56,050
Arrange a banquet?

215
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:00,160
Grandma Chen is confused.

216
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,250
You know that.

217
00:08:01,690 --> 00:08:02,720
She's recognized Mr. Zhang

218
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,040
as her son

219
00:08:04,400 --> 00:08:05,650
and wants him to get married.

220
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:07,760
So,

221
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,000
I...

222
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:13,920
You agreed?

223
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:24,760
But

224
00:08:24,890 --> 00:08:26,360
I also want to hear your opinion.

225
00:08:30,330 --> 00:08:31,170
Mom,

226
00:08:32,090 --> 00:08:33,570
at first, I did oppose

227
00:08:33,570 --> 00:08:35,050
you and Mr. Zhang being together.

228
00:08:39,930 --> 00:08:41,120
But over time,

229
00:08:42,050 --> 00:08:43,220
I've seen him do a lot for you

230
00:08:43,290 --> 00:08:44,930
and for our family.

231
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:48,120
I believe he is sincere.

232
00:08:52,690 --> 00:08:54,570
Even if it's not for Grandma Chen,

233
00:08:54,820 --> 00:08:56,340
even if you really want to get married,

234
00:08:58,640 --> 00:09:00,090
I'll fully support you.

235
00:09:11,290 --> 00:09:12,170
Mom,

236
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:13,440
I know

237
00:09:13,810 --> 00:09:15,450
you've suffered a lot

238
00:09:16,170 --> 00:09:17,290
because of me.

239
00:09:19,810 --> 00:09:20,880
Other classmates' parents

240
00:09:21,690 --> 00:09:23,930
go home after work to watch TV dramas,

241
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,090
go for a walk,

242
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,690
or play cards.

243
00:09:28,580 --> 00:09:29,420
You're the only one

244
00:09:29,690 --> 00:09:31,530
who has to work another job after work,

245
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,570
and you don't get any rest on holidays.

246
00:09:36,090 --> 00:09:37,600
I don't want you to be so tired.

247
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,080
Mom,

248
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:44,360
you've worked so hard.

249
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:49,400
I used to think

250
00:09:49,410 --> 00:09:50,330
that when I grew up,

251
00:09:50,930 --> 00:09:52,210
I could use my own ability

252
00:09:52,210 --> 00:09:53,600
to take care of you and protect you.

253
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:55,880
This is also my promise to Dad.

254
00:10:01,570 --> 00:10:02,880
You were so young.

255
00:10:03,210 --> 00:10:04,760
What did you know about promises?

256
00:10:05,210 --> 00:10:06,810
But in my heart, it was a promise.

257
00:10:09,770 --> 00:10:11,200
Later, I realized

258
00:10:14,630 --> 00:10:16,530
that there were many things

259
00:10:17,760 --> 00:10:19,090
that I could not do as a son.

260
00:10:22,090 --> 00:10:23,290
But Mr. Zhang could.

261
00:10:28,330 --> 00:10:29,760
So apart from

262
00:10:31,170 --> 00:10:33,120
keeping my promise to Dad,

263
00:10:35,170 --> 00:10:36,410
of course, I hope you

264
00:10:36,410 --> 00:10:37,720
pursue your own happiness.

265
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:52,090
What are you doing?
I'm not trying to be emotional.

266
00:10:53,760 --> 00:10:54,690
No more crying.

267
00:11:01,530 --> 00:11:03,290
Alright, go out.

268
00:11:03,290 --> 00:11:04,130
Don't stay inside.

269
00:11:55,930 --> 00:11:56,770
Aiping,

270
00:11:57,050 --> 00:11:58,000
let's discuss something.

271
00:11:58,040 --> 00:11:59,490
The Oriental Pearl Tower is the best.

272
00:11:59,640 --> 00:12:01,050
Jinjiang Hotel is also good.

273
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:02,600
But the hall in Jinjiang Hotel

274
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:03,440
is too small.

275
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:06,360
International Hotel has a nice setting.

276
00:12:06,760 --> 00:12:07,880
But I've asked

277
00:12:07,880 --> 00:12:08,760
about it.

278
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:09,960
It'll be two months

279
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,050
before I can book it.

280
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:12,720
I'll call back

281
00:12:12,930 --> 00:12:13,840
to confirm again,

282
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:15,090
and see if they can

283
00:12:15,410 --> 00:12:16,570
cut us a line or something.

284
00:12:16,690 --> 00:12:17,530
What do you think?

285
00:12:18,530 --> 00:12:19,370
Qiming,

286
00:12:19,530 --> 00:12:21,220
don't you need a marriage certificate

287
00:12:21,220 --> 00:12:22,240
to book the banquet?

288
00:12:22,810 --> 00:12:23,650
