00:23:46,980 --> 00:23:48,660
Can you do me a favor?

582
00:23:50,420 --> 00:23:51,340
Go pick out

583
00:23:51,660 --> 00:23:53,260
the biggest and heaviest set

584
00:23:53,360 --> 00:23:54,340
of yellow jewelry.

585
00:23:58,260 --> 00:24:00,100
Grandma, you hide the key too?

586
00:24:03,340 --> 00:24:05,340
There won't be
straw paper inside, right?

587
00:24:05,540 --> 00:24:07,140
How could it be straw paper?

588
00:24:08,060 --> 00:24:08,900
Look.

589
00:24:12,820 --> 00:24:15,140
There's a lot of money inside.

590
00:24:15,580 --> 00:24:17,140
The password is your birthday.

591
00:24:19,420 --> 00:24:20,580
My birthday?

592
00:24:22,660 --> 00:24:23,540
You take this

593
00:24:23,540 --> 00:24:25,620
and go pick out the biggest
and heaviest set.

594
00:24:25,820 --> 00:24:27,420
It doesn't matter if you use up

595
00:24:27,420 --> 00:24:28,300
all the money inside.

596
00:24:28,420 --> 00:24:29,260
I still have money.

597
00:24:32,380 --> 00:24:33,980
Don't doubt that.

598
00:24:34,180 --> 00:24:36,300
I've even prepared your dowry.

599
00:24:36,580 --> 00:24:37,420
The dowry?

600
00:24:37,580 --> 00:24:38,420
Of course.

601
00:24:39,100 --> 00:24:40,380
Men and women have to get married

602
00:24:40,380 --> 00:24:41,180
when they grow up.

603
00:24:41,270 --> 00:24:42,140
Sooner or later,

604
00:24:42,140 --> 00:24:43,540
you'll have to get married.

605
00:24:44,540 --> 00:24:45,380
But

606
00:24:47,100 --> 00:24:49,420
you can't talk to the nanny outside

607
00:24:49,820 --> 00:24:51,580
about getting money for shopping.

608
00:24:52,300 --> 00:24:53,340
She's not reliable.

609
00:24:53,580 --> 00:24:54,420
Got it?

610
00:24:54,580 --> 00:24:56,860
Especially not the password.

611
00:24:57,660 --> 00:24:59,060
The password is your birthday.

612
00:24:59,740 --> 00:25:00,580
- Okay.
- Go ahead.

613
00:25:06,060 --> 00:25:07,100
Alright.

614
00:25:07,820 --> 00:25:09,300
I get it, okay.

615
00:25:09,380 --> 00:25:10,980
If it can't be changed, so be it.

616
00:25:11,260 --> 00:25:12,100
I'm hanging up.

617
00:25:12,860 --> 00:25:13,700
Baby.

618
00:25:16,860 --> 00:25:17,860
So mysterious.

619
00:25:17,860 --> 00:25:19,020
What did she ask you to do?

620
00:25:20,060 --> 00:25:21,540
Grandma gave me a bank card.

621
00:25:21,900 --> 00:25:23,500
She asked me to buy the biggest

622
00:25:23,500 --> 00:25:24,860
and heaviest set

623
00:25:25,180 --> 00:25:26,300
of yellow jewelry.

624
00:25:26,870 --> 00:25:27,550
Mom,

625
00:25:27,550 --> 00:25:28,920
what exactly is yellow jewelry?

626
00:25:29,100 --> 00:25:30,580
It's gold.

627
00:25:32,140 --> 00:25:33,900
She may be forgetful,

628
00:25:34,040 --> 00:25:35,890
but she's very generous
to her daughter-in-law.

629
00:25:36,820 --> 00:25:38,060
How much money is in it?

630
00:25:38,740 --> 00:25:39,820
Grandma said it's a lot.

631
00:25:40,180 --> 00:25:41,220
She also said the password

632
00:25:41,220 --> 00:25:42,340
for this card is my birthday.

633
00:25:44,580 --> 00:25:45,540
Baby, here.

634
00:25:46,340 --> 00:25:47,740
Let me keep the card.

635
00:25:47,820 --> 00:25:48,860
I'll buy it later, okay?

636
00:25:48,860 --> 00:25:49,700
Okay.

637
00:25:50,980 --> 00:25:51,820
Baby,

638
00:25:54,100 --> 00:25:56,340
I have one more thing to tell you.

639
00:25:57,100 --> 00:25:59,100
It's about your Auntie Aiping's wedding.

640
00:25:59,420 --> 00:26:00,540
It's scheduled

641
00:26:00,740 --> 00:26:02,540
on the day of your birthday.

642
00:26:02,820 --> 00:26:04,820
They booked it in a hurry,

643
00:26:04,820 --> 00:26:06,820
so they didn't have any other date.

644
00:26:07,660 --> 00:26:08,500
So...

645
00:26:09,580 --> 00:26:10,580
It's okay.

646
00:26:11,580 --> 00:26:13,260
It's not a big date anyway.

647
00:26:13,260 --> 00:26:14,500
I didn't plan to celebrate.

648
00:26:16,300 --> 00:26:17,380
I mean

649
00:26:17,380 --> 00:26:18,900
there will be a lot of people

650
00:26:20,020 --> 00:26:21,180
that day.

651
00:26:21,180 --> 00:26:22,540
Over 20 tables.

652
00:26:23,300 --> 00:26:25,540
A lot of adults and kids

653
00:26:26,340 --> 00:26:27,340
will be there,

654
00:26:27,660 --> 00:26:29,540
so we'll meet a lot of people.

655
00:26:30,860 --> 00:26:31,700
Baby,

656
00:26:31,740 --> 00:26:32,820
I'll give you money.

657
00:26:32,820 --> 00:26:34,820
How about you
treat your classmates to a meal

658
00:26:35,180 --> 00:26:36,300
and you all

659
00:26:36,300 --> 00:26:37,540
have a lively birthday?

660
00:26:38,100 --> 00:26:39,100
It's okay, Mom.

661
00:26:39,500 --> 00:26:40,340
I'll go.

662
00:26:42,900 --> 00:26:44,100
Alright, okay.

663
00:27:00,820 --> 00:27:02,820
Zhang Qiming made a big move this time.

664
00:27:03,100 --> 00:27:04,860
He even reserved the whole venue.

665
00:27:05,260 --> 00:27:07,300
After so many years,
they finally get married.

666
00:27:07,340 --> 00:27:08,820
Of course, they want to show off.

667
00:27:09,260 --> 00:27:10,100
Mom,

668
00:27:10,860 --> 00:27:12,340
have Mr. Zhang and Mrs. Xiao

669
00:27:12,340 --> 00:27:13,620
set their wedding date?

670
00:27:13,710 --> 00:27:14,560
Yes, they have.

671
00:27:14,580 --> 00:27:15,420
This Sunday.

672
00:27:17,260 --> 00:27:19,100
But it's Qian Jiayue's birthday.

673
00:27:19,820 --> 00:27:20,660
Really?

674
00:27:20,980 --> 00:27:21,820
Yeah.

675
00:27:22,020 --> 00:27:23,020
I'm buying her a present

676
00:27:23,020 --> 00:27:24,180
in Xidian Mall this afternoon.

677
00:27:29,860 --> 00:27:33,420
(Xidian Mall, Tian's Gift Shop)

678
00:27:33,420 --> 00:27:34,260
Hello, Boss.

679
00:27:34,400 --> 00:27:35,280
Hello.

680
00:27:35,300 --> 00:27:36,780
I'd like to buy a gift.

681
00:27:37,580 --> 00:27:38,620
Let's take a look inside.

682
00:27:39,580 --> 00:27:40,740
Is it for a boy or a girl?

683
00:27:40,980 --> 00:27:41,820
For a girl.

684
00:27:42,820 --> 00:27:43,660
A girl?

685
00:27:44,060 --> 00:27:45,140
Take a look here.

686
00:27:45,900 --> 00:27:46,740
Who is she to you?

687
00:27:46,740 --> 00:27:47,620
Let me recommend it.

688
00:27:48,820 --> 00:27:49,660
Someone

689
00:27:49,820 --> 00:27:50,740
special.

690
00:27:51,020 --> 00:27:52,340
Is it a birthday gift or...?

691
00:27:52,340 --> 00:27:53,340
Not a birthday gift.

692
00:27:54,980 --> 00:27:55,820
It's the kind of gift

693
00:27:56,140 --> 00:27:57,420
that says

694
00:27:58,420 --> 00:28:00,660
"You mean a lot to me".

695
00:28:01,780 --> 00:28:03,580
Do you know what she likes?

696
00:28:04,380 --> 00:28:05,220
She likes

697
00:28:07,860 --> 00:28:08,700
to eat.

698
00:28:09,300 --> 00:28:10,140
That's easy.

699
00:28:10,380 --> 00:28:11,220
Over here.

700
00:28:11,340 --> 00:28:12,660
Look, this is my shop too.

701
00:28:12,820 --> 00:28:13,780
Come and have a look.

702
00:28:17,140 --> 00:28:18,780
Give her some chocolates.

703
00:28:19,500 --> 00:28:21,100
Girls love them.

704
00:28:21,180 --> 00:28:22,260
This is the perfect one.

705
00:28:22,900 --> 00:28:24,580
Check out these new arrivals.

706
00:28:25,660 --> 00:28:26,900
You can even match the gift box.

707
00:28:27,140 --> 00:28:27,980
Pick it out yourself.

708
00:28:28,180 --> 00:28:29,420
It shows your sincerity.

709
00:28:30,090 --> 00:28:31,200
- They're all good.
- Okay.

710
00:28:31,340 --> 00:28:32,180
I'll take my pick.

711
00:28:32,820 --> 00:28:33,660
I want that one.

712
00:28:34,620 --> 00:28:35,660
- Which one?
- That one.

713
00:28:35,860 --> 00:28:36,700
The heart-shaped one,

714
00:28:37,100 --> 00:28:37,940
the pink one.

715
00:28:38,240 --> 00:28:39,100
That's the one, right?

716
00:28:39,340 --> 00:28:40,180
Yes.

717
00:28:40,380 --> 00:28:41,220
This looks nice.

718
00:28:41,220 --> 00:28:42,340
Girls would love it.

719
00:28:43,340 --> 00:28:44,180
Alright.

720
00:28:44,660 --> 00:28:45,500
Take your pick.

721
00:28:46,180 --> 00:28:47,060
Anything here, right?

722
00:28:47,060 --> 00:28:47,910
Yes.

723
00:28:47,920 --> 00:28:48,860
White chocolate,

724
00:28:48,860 --> 00:28:49,700
dark chocolate,

725
00:28:49,780 --> 00:28:50,620
and this filled one

726
00:28:51,140 --> 00:28:52,260
sell exceptionally well.

727
00:28:53,900 --> 00:28:56,940
(Shanghai Puyang No. 2 Middle School)

728
00:29:25,910 --> 00:29:27,500
Ka Men, can I borrow a pen?

729
00:29:29,700 --> 00:29:30,580
Just a moment.

730
00:29:32,020 --> 00:29:33,020
This blue one.

731
00:29:33,100 --> 00:29:34,180
It writes beautifully.

732
00:29:34,340 --> 00:29:35,180
Thanks.

733
00:29:48,780 --> 00:29:49,620
Thank you.

734
00:29:58,980 --> 00:29:59,820
Bye.

735
00:30:22,580 --> 00:30:23,420
Lu Yao?

736
00:30:24,580 --> 00:30:25,420
Rui,

737
00:30:25,820 --> 00:30:27,100
I heard from my mom

738
00:30:27,840 --> 00:30:29,130
that your family is going abroad.

739
00:30:29,780 --> 00:30:30,620
Yeah,

740
00:30:30,640 --> 00:30:31,840
I've been here for a few days.

741
00:30:31,840 --> 00:30:33,190
I haven't had a chance to tell you.

742
00:30:33,490 --> 00:30:35,260
You know my uncle lives in Australia.

743
00:30:35,260 --> 00:30:37,740
I'm planning
to pursue a master's degree.

744
00:30:37,820 --> 00:30:39,100
How long is it?

745
00:30:39,260 --> 00:30:40,120
Two years.

746
00:30:40,140 --> 00:30:41,380
So you'll be back in two years?

747
00:30:41,380 --> 00:30:42,220
I'm not sure.

748
00:30:42,780 --> 00:30:44,780
I might go for a PhD,

749
00:30:44,980 --> 00:30:46,860
or I might find a job there.

750
00:30:47,380 --> 00:30:48,780
There's also a chance I'll return.

751
00:30:49,380 --> 00:30:50,220
What's up?

752
00:30:50,980 --> 00:30:52,180
I got you a gift.

753
00:30:55,020 --> 00:30:55,860
Here,

754
00:30:56,180 --> 00:30:57,020
this is for you.

755
00:30:57,580 --> 00:30:58,420
Open it.

756
00:30:59,380 --> 00:31:00,580
I picked these

757
00:31:00,580 --> 00:31:01,500
one by one.

758
00:31:02,870 --> 00:31:04,100
It represents my feelings.

759
00:31:05,220 --> 00:31:08,140
(Special gift for special one)

760
00:31:16,300 --> 00:31:17,140
Thank you.

761
00:31:19,780 --> 00:31:21,820
But I really can't accept this.

762
00:31:23,060 --> 00:31:23,980
Please take it back.

763
00:31:24,660 --> 00:31:25,500
This...

764
00:31:26,780 --> 00:31:27,620
Take it back.

765
00:31:39,260 --> 00:31:40,100
Go home quickly.

766
00:31:40,180 --> 00:31:41,300
What are you standing here?

767
00:32:20,580 --> 00:32:21,420
But...

768
00:32:21,560 --> 00:32:22,950
But Senior Xue is...

769
00:32:25,200 --> 00:32:26,040
You...

770
00:32:26,870 --> 00:32:28,740
You knew her before?

771
00:32:29,620 --> 00:32:31,260
We grew up together.

772
00:32:32,900 --> 00:32:34,260
She was my neighbor.

773
00:32:35,760 --> 00:32:37,140
As far back as I remember,

774
00:32:37,860 --> 00:32:39,020
she's been

775
00:32:39,700 --> 00:32:40,780
gentle

776
00:32:41,710 --> 00:32:43,260
and pretty.

777
00:32:43,880 --> 00:32:44,900
She played with

778
00:32:44,900 --> 00:32:46,300
a few kids from my building.

779
00:32:47,570 --> 00:32:48,410
She...

780
00:32:48,440 --> 00:32:49,920
She let me play rubber band skipping

781
00:32:49,920 --> 00:32:50,460
with her

782
00:32:51,540 --> 00:32:52,820
and taught us to recognize words.

783
00:32:54,340 --> 00:32:56,100
Whenever we were mischievous,

784
00:32:56,100 --> 00:32:57,380
she never got angry.

785
00:32:58,020 --> 00:32:59,140
She was always smiling

786
00:32:59,830 --> 00:33:00,820
and happy.

787
00:33:02,860 --> 00:33:04,340
I used to stutter when I was little,

788
00:33:05,060 --> 00:33:07,000
so she encouraged me
to try out as a little host.

789
00:33:07,710 --> 00:33:09,080
Have you heard of Little Star?

790
00:33:09,780 --> 00:33:10,780
I still remember

791
00:33:11,060 --> 00:33:12,180
that she gave me a tie

792
00:33:12,180 --> 00:33:13,660
when I first appeared

793
00:33:14,620 --> 00:33:15,980
on stage as a host.

794
00:33:17,000 --> 00:33:18,260
I still keep it to this day.

795
00:33:18,740 --> 00:33:21,100
I'm tonight's host, Liu Wanqing.

796
00:33:21,100 --> 00:33:23,420
(Happy Reunion, Happy New Year)
I'm tonight's host, Lu Yao.

797
00:33:23,650 --> 00:33:24,500
Lu Yao,

798
00:33:24,500 --> 00:33:26,740
1990 is about to arrive.

799
00:33:26,860 --> 00:33:28,420
Do you have any New Year wishes?

800
00:33:28,620 --> 00:33:30,580
I wish for long-lasting friendships

801
00:33:30,780 --> 00:33:34,100
with my classmates and friends.

802
00:33:38,860 --> 00:33:40,180
Later, she went to college.

803
00:33:43,090 --> 00:33:44,340
Her family moved away too.

804
00:33:46,380 --> 00:33:47,540
I haven't seen her

805
00:33:48,680 --> 00:33:50,860
for two years and three months.

806
00:33:52,570 --> 00:33:53,500
When she came back

807
00:33:54,680 --> 00:33:56,140
to our school for exchanges,

808
00:33:57,240 --> 00:33:58,300
it was like a switch

809
00:33:58,300 --> 00:33:59,660
was flipped.

810
00:34:00,660 --> 00:34:02,780
Every day, I was so happy.

811
00:34:02,980 --> 00:34:03,820
I looked forward

812
00:34:03,820 --> 00:34:05,500
to seeing her at school every day.

813
00:34:07,580 --> 00:34:08,420
However,

814
00:34:10,980 --> 00:34:12,220
she was going abroad

815
00:34:12,900 --> 00:34:13,860
after the exchange.

816
00:34:18,580 --> 00:34:19,460
It's very likely

817
00:34:22,380 --> 00:34:23,860
that we'll never meet again.

818
00:34:28,410 --> 00:34:29,900
I gave her chocolates,

819
00:34:30,670 --> 00:34:31,940
but they were returned. Tell me,

820
00:34:33,070 --> 00:34:34,840
am I being ridiculous?

821
00:34:37,060 --> 00:34:37,940
No, you're not.

822
00:34:39,260 --> 00:34:40,620
Not at all.

823
00:34:49,420 --> 00:34:50,460
I've thought long and hard.

824
00:34:52,460 --> 00:34:53,860
The only thing I can do

825
00:34:54,750 --> 00:34:56,500
is to give her a farewell gift.

826
00:34:59,180 --> 00:35:00,900
At least it shows my feelings.

827
00:35:13,770 --> 00:35:14,980
Maybe...

828
00:35:22,600 --> 00:35:24,100
Maybe I can help you.

829
00:35:33,430 --> 00:35:34,270
Liu Wanqing.

830
00:35:36,580 --> 00:35:37,540
Senior Xue.

831
00:35:40,660 --> 00:35:41,860
What do you want to see me?

832
00:35:43,100 --> 00:35:44,780
I heard you're going abroad.

833
00:35:45,350 --> 00:35:46,220
Yes.

834
00:35:46,220 --> 00:35:48,180
I'm leaving right after this exchange.

835
00:35:52,300 --> 00:35:53,740
I'm especially happy to be back

836
00:35:53,980 --> 00:35:54,940
at No. 2 Middle School

837
00:35:55,020 --> 00:35:56,660
for the exchange and to meet you all.

838
00:35:56,980 --> 00:35:58,500
But it's almost senior year.

839
00:35:58,860 --> 00:36:00,060
You have to work hard.

840
00:36:02,580 --> 00:36:03,540
Senior Xue,

841
00:36:03,780 --> 00:36:05,860
you're so gentle.

842
00:36:07,460 --> 00:36:08,580
You're very nice too.

843
00:36:08,580 --> 00:36:09,540
You know I'm leaving,

844
00:36:09,540 --> 00:36:10,570
so you came to see me off.

845
00:36:11,260 --> 00:36:12,100
Thank you.

846
00:36:16,580 --> 00:36:17,940
Anything else?

847
00:36:19,700 --> 00:36:21,620
I heard from Lu Yao
that you're neighbors.

848
00:36:22,230 --> 00:36:23,140
Yes, we are.

849
00:36:25,800 --> 00:36:26,640
That's right.

850
00:36:26,790 --> 00:36:28,260
You're in the same class, right?

851
00:36:31,020 --> 00:36:31,900
Actually,

852
00:36:32,460 --> 00:36:34,100
I'm here to deliver something

853
00:36:34,100 --> 00:36:34,940
for Lu Yao.

854
00:36:42,620 --> 00:36:44,100
I already told him I don't need it.

855
00:36:46,260 --> 00:36:47,260
But it's a farewell gift

856
00:36:47,620 --> 00:36:49,060
Lu Yao had picked out

857
00:36:49,060 --> 00:36:49,900
with care.

858
00:36:49,980 --> 00:36:51,100
The chocolates in here

859
00:36:51,100 --> 00:36:53,380
were handpicked by him one by one.

860
00:36:53,780 --> 00:36:54,620
He...

861
00:36:56,100 --> 00:36:57,420
If you don't accept it,

862
00:36:57,660 --> 00:36:59,570
he'll be very sad and upset.

863
00:37:00,900 --> 00:37:02,260
Senior Xue, please accept it.

864
00:37:06,660 --> 00:37:08,900
Then thank Lu Yao for me.

865
00:37:10,100 --> 00:37:10,940
She really took it?

866
00:37:12,100 --> 00:37:12,940
She did.

867
00:37:12,940 --> 00:37:14,100
What did she say?

868
00:37:15,260 --> 00:37:16,100
She...

869
00:37:16,300 --> 00:37:17,140
She said

870
00:37:18,380 --> 00:37:19,220
thank you,

871
00:37:19,980 --> 00:37:21,780
that she appreciated your thoughts,

872
00:37:22,620 --> 00:37:24,140
and that she felt happy.

873
00:37:24,870 --> 00:37:26,280
